## Non-Negotiable Rules

1. Imports → always `@/`. Never `../../..`.
2. Strings → never hardcode user-visible text in JSX. Use `useTranslations()`. Update all locale files (`messages/en.json`, `he.json`, `es.json`, `ar.json`).
3. Data reads → `useFetch`. Data writes → `useMutation`. Never `fetch`/`axios` directly in components.
4. Routes → never hardcode strings. Use `WEB_ROUTES` and `API_ROUTES` constants.
5. Forms → never raw `<input>/<select>/<textarea>`. Use `src/components/form` components.
6. Config → never `process.env` in components. Use `CONFIG` from `@/lib/app-config`.
7. Storage → never `localStorage` directly. Use `useLocalStorage` / `getStorage` / `setStorage`.
8. Toasts → never `toast()` directly. Use `toastSuccess/Error/Warning/Info/Promise` from `@/lib/toast`.
9. Buttons → never raw `<button>`. Use `<Button>` from `@/components/ui/button`.
10. Text → never raw `<p>/<h1>–<h6>/<span>`. Use `<Typography variant="...">` from `@/components/ui/typography`.
11. Stores → never add Zustand fields unless state is shared across unrelated components.
12. Tables → use `<DataTable>` from `@/components/ui/data-table`. No custom sort/filter/pagination state.
